Las Vegas Sands Corp. (LVS) â€™s China unit,
the casino operator expanding with resorts and casinos in Macau,
is expected to sign a $3.7 billion loan today, according to a
person familiar with the matter.  About 10 percent of the five-year loan was sold in general
