BNP Paribas SA, Citigroup Inc, Commerzbank AG, Credit Agricole
CIB, Credit Suisse Group AG, Goldman Sachs Group Inc, Industrial
& Commercial Bank of China Macau Ltd., ING Groep NV, Sumitomo
Mitsui Financial Group Inc., UBS AG and United Overseas Bank
Ltd. are the global coordinators on the underwritten facility,
another person familiar with the matter said on Sept. 6.  Banco Nacional Ultramarino SA, Bank of Nova Scotia, DBS
Bank Ltd., Oversea-Chinese Banking Corp. and Wing Lung Bank also
